Package hsrt.mec.controldeveloper.core.com.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICommand
    Interface ICommand defines the method for naming commands.
    IDirection
    Interface IDirection defines the interface for a direction command, i.e. the degree, in which the mobile device shall be turned.
    IGear
    Interface IGear defines the interface for a gear command, i.e. the speed and the duraration of the mobile device.
    IPause
    Interface IPause defines the interface for a pause command, i.e. the duraration, how long the mobile device shall be paused.
